{"tid":697675,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六七暴動期間，少年曾德成於學校派傳單，煽動罪成，判監2年","createTime":"2018-06-11T06:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T06:30:28.000Z","uid":13100,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a033ebfc4f25e5fd128d10764e7757536649e48a","tid":697675,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:10:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140705/52661601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140705%2F52661601&d=fcGQngY%2Blzav3npzg1sOopUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=02cbfe56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140705%2F52661601&h=aad5b12b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140705/52661601</a><br />\n六七暴動期間，18歲的曾德成是聖保羅學院預科學生，他於同年9月28日在校內派發派發宣傳共產主義及反港英政府傳單，內容包括譴責當時香港教育制度的目的是「推行奴化教育」（The education system aiming at enslavement），及批評當年港英政府「不准我們愛國」、「用法西斯手段鎮壓愛國同胞」。<br />\n<br />\n當時英國籍代校長韋爾思報警，曾德成被到校的警員拘捕，他於同年10月9日因煽動罪名被判監禁2年，成為少年犯及留有案底，失去升讀大學機會。當年法官在判詞中指曾德成愚蠢，又指其行為是自毀前途，與人無尤，但當時曾德成的父親在庭上表示兒子「做得很對」。"},{"pid":"4dfa1a830cf53e9dacab185ff412c1d1457e13d7","tid":697675,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:12:10.000Z","msg":"有父陰"},{"pid":"d6c68702526b405c605fbbb6d1d0d0efc95c7ec6","tid":697675,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"港英政府同支共政府分別<br />\n<br />\n你諗下支共政府底下，坐6年出獄之後會點？<br />\n<br />\n望望劉霞劉曉波你就明<br />\n<br />\n無前途嫁啦天琦BB"},{"pid":"4cb050bdc0c20ac82629f09dcf1ba5bd62af4c3b","tid":697675,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d6c68702526b405c605fbbb6d1d0d0efc95c7ec6","tid":697675,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"港英政府同支共政府分別<br />\n<br />\n你諗下支共政府底下，坐6年出獄之後會點？<br />\n<br />\n望望劉霞劉曉波你就明<br />\n<b